{"TopicId":180466,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Stock transfer window planner","CreatedByName":"EchoLima","CreatedById":61992,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-10T00:06:35Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"EchoLima","CreatedById":61992,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-10T00:06:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow that we\u0027re getting a delta-v indicator, we need a stock transfer window planner. There should be a window in map view that asks for the transfer origin and destination planets, which then displays delta-v requirements and other information (like the relative angle of the destination planet). The time to the next transfer window should also be displayed, along with two buttons- one that says something like \u0022warp now\u0022, and the other that says \u0022set reminder\u0022. The reminder would work by using the stock message system, and would display a pop up a certain amount of time before the window opens (maybe a day before).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAn example of this is in the spoiler:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cu\u003ETransfer Window Planner\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EXfer Origin: [\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#f39c12;\u0022\u003EChoose from menu\u003C/span\u003E]\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EXfer Destination: [\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#f39c12;\u0022\u003EChoose from menu\u003C/span\u003E]\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003E-----------------------------------------------------------\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EInjection delta-v: xx m/s\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EInsertion delta-v: xx m/s\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EAngle: xx\u00B0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003E-----------------------------------------------------------\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003ENext window: x days, x hours, x minutes\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003E[\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#f39c12;\u0022\u003EWarp now\u003C/span\u003E] [\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#f39c12;\u0022\u003ESet reminder\u003C/span\u003E]\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003EI know that there already are transfer window planner mods; this is my idea for a simplified stock one.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-12-10T00:10:36Z\u0022 title=\u002212/10/2018 12:10  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 10, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by EchoLima\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-10T00:57:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nConsidering that this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed3724769277\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/84005-14x-transfer-window-planner-v1630-march-18/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:227px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs made by a member of Squad staff, I don\u0027t see why it couldn\u0027t be added to the base game part and parcel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-10T03:15:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223502372\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180466\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221544403439\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rocket In My Pocket\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Rocket In My Pocket said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nConsidering that this is made by a member of Squad staff, I don\u0027t see why it couldn\u0027t be added to the base game part and parcel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve been saying that since they joined Squad.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-15T21:07:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is still desperately needed in stock. Hint hint. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kspnerd122","CreatedById":199169,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-17T13:47:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSKWOD please add this, this will be loved by literally every player ever\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}